sday: Read Study Helps assignment. </div><div class="t m9e9 x7 h13 y1868 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Friday: </div><div class="t m1f3 x76 he y55a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review the entire lesson. </div><div class="t mc38 x6d h13 y5e5 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction </div><div class="t m6fd x4a he y72 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the midst of all the destruction of the </div><div class="t me08 x17 he ybf7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">last days, God&apos;s people will have a song of </div><div class="t m10fc x17 he y112 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trust and confidence. All things earthly will </div><div class="t m365 x17 he y58f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fail, the world itself will reel and be dis-</div><div class="t m7f4 x17 he y5c7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">solved, but with faith God&apos;s people exclaim: </div><div class="t m5a3 x17 he y428 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;We have a strong city.&quot; They have not </div><div class="t m3d9 x17 he y42b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">been perfect, but they have made God their </div><div class="t m9be x17 he y42e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trust, and all is well. </div><div class="t m2ba4 x6f h13 y1397 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Confidence and Trust </div><div class="t m8fe x5d he yb67 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. What song will be sung &quot;in that </div><div class="t m169a x17 he y5bf ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">day&quot;? To whom will the gates be </div><div class="t mbdb x17 he y3f9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">opened? Isa. 26:1, 2. See Rev. 22:14. </div><div class="t m294e x3e h13 y152 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson Outline: </div><div class="t m2dd x3e h13 y402 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction </div><div class="t m9f2 x3e h13 y154 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. Confidence and Trust </div><div class="t m1048 x64 he y5fa ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m98a xc he ydd ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A song of assurance. Isa. 26:1, 2. </div><div class="t m1f3 x64 he y1d7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t ma69 xc h